Package com.example.infinimood.controller

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BitmapCallback
    Interface for bitmap callbacks, to be implemented by any methods needing a callback with a bitmap value
    BooleanCallback
    Interface for boolean callbacks, to be implemented by any methods needing a callback with a boolean value
    DatePickerCallback
    Interface for date callbacks, to be implemented by any methods needing a callback with date information
    FilterCallback
    FilterCallback An interface for users callbacks, to be implemented by any methods needing a callback with a list of filtered items
    GetMoodCallback
    GetMoodCallback An interface for mood callbacks, to be implemented by any methods needing a callback with Mood information
    GetMoodsCallback
    GetMoodsCallback An interface for moods callbacks, to be implemented by any methods needing a callback with a list of Moods.
    GetUsersCallback
    GetUsersCallback An interface for users callbacks, to be implemented by any methods needing a callback with a list of Users.
    StringCallback
    StringCallback An interface for string callbacks, to be implemented by any methods needing a callback with string data.
    TimePickerCallback
    TimePickerCallback An interface for Time callbacks, to be implemented by any methods needing a callback with a Time data.
